description: "This early 18th century map of Batavia (Jakarta) shows an important port city, with military forts, a long pier, and many ships at sea. However, the map also shows a city surrounded by fields and plantations, for producing crops and grazing animals."
label: "Les isles de la Sonde Moluques Philippines, Carolines, et Mariannes / par le S. Robert de Vaugondy &c. ; grave̓ par E. Dussy."
